{"tid":277034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭智左眼骨折　隨時變盲","createTime":"2017-06-09T09:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T18:25:49.000Z","uid":31314,"like":221,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ea7de1e20bc4ac0c382b9ab32c2b02d707ab3c","tid":277034,"uid":31314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:36:16.000Z","msg":"中國國家隊隊長鄭智眼部骨折，隨時變盲！下周國足對敍利亞進行世界盃亞洲區外圍賽，但鄭智沒有隨隊備戰，國內傳媒爆料，原來鄭智左眼受傷，如強行操練，最嚴重會失明。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來，於同菲律賓比賽前一日訓練中，鄭智左眼意外被隊友撞傷，眼部還出現了骨折。當時鄭智感覺到只要眼球轉動，頭部都會極度疼痛。鄭智立刻喺隊醫陪同下連夜前往醫院進行檢查。經過檢查顯示，鄭智的左眼出現骨折，而且眼睛裡有非常一塊細微嘅小塊骨頭，呢個亦係鄭智只要一轉動眼珠就會非常疼痛的原因。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"1ce7cb1f135dc6cc1daa0850172458edf1eb4a17","tid":277034,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:37:04.000Z","msg":"已成功評分"},{"pid":"bd529d24af78926c3043fe45f84bdfe3862734cf","tid":277034,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:09:34.000Z","msg":"你已正評了這評論"},{"pid":"7a5553b853d89d3cdb8e22e362509c1d8e92b12d","tid":277034,"uid":66129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:13:46.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"b1126d8bd340d731c51653b8645f6f6165e497e3","tid":277034,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30704b8129c6add93cec5074e72c341c1132750","tid":277034,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:18:44.000Z","msg":"被隊友撞傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd8485